org.hps.record.triggerbank

Class VTPFEETrigger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.record.triggerbank.VTPFEETrigger

  • public class VTPFEETrigger
extends Object
    Class VTPFEETrigger Parse HPS FEE Trigger of VTP and store information. HPS FEE Trigger:
    • 10bit [0 : 9] trigger time in 4 ns unit
    • 7bit [10 : 16] bit mask specify which FEE regions (ECal x-ranges) triggered the system
